dando consejos sobre problemas amorosos.

116
00:06:33,255 --> 00:06:35,655
Nuestro hermano menor, 'Tee Lek',

117
00:06:35,955 --> 00:06:36,955
o 'Tee',

118
00:06:37,605 --> 00:06:39,945
