141
00:07:32,315 --> 00:07:36,885
- temblor, temblor, temblor, temblor.
- Temblor, temblor, temblor.

142
00:07:36,925 --> 00:07:37,895
Estos dos hermanos

143
00:07:38,125 --> 00:07:40,005
Son simplemente desquiciados.

144
00:07:41,485 --> 00:07:42,575
- ¡O!
- ¡O!

145
00:07:45,445 --> 00:07:46,055
Fue,

146
00:07:46,255 --> 00:07:47,575
¿Me puedes dar 2.000 baht?

147
00:07:47,855 --> 00:07:49,095
Espera, Tee.

148
00:07:49,185 --> 00:07:50,645
